<LawDetailResponse>
  <law>
    <mst>001</mst>
    <lawId>LSA001</lawId>
    <title>산업안전보건법</title>
    <shortTitle>산안법</shortTitle>
    <promulgationDate>2024-01-09</promulgationDate>
    <enforcementDate>2024-01-09</enforcementDate>
    <sourceUrl>https://open.law.go.kr/LSA001</sourceUrl>
  </law>
  <articles>
    <article>
      <articleNo>제1조</articleNo>
      <title>목적</title>
      <body>산업안전보건 기준을 확립하여 근로자의 안전과 보건을 유지·증진한다.</body>
      <effectiveFrom>2024-01-09</effectiveFrom>
    </article>
    <article>
      <articleNo>제10조</articleNo>
      <title>안전조치</title>
      <body>사업주는 필요한 안전조치를 하여야 한다.</body>
      <effectiveFrom>2024-01-09</effectiveFrom>
      <paragraphs>
        <paragraph>
          <paragraphNo>1</paragraphNo>
          <body>사업주는 기계·기구에 대한 방호조치를 하여야 한다.</body>
          <effectiveFrom>2024-01-09</effectiveFrom>
          <items>
            <item>
              <itemNo>1</itemNo>
              <body>덮개를 설치한다.</body>
              <effectiveFrom>2024-01-09</effectiveFrom>
            </item>
          </items>
        </paragraph>
      </paragraphs>
    </article>
    <article>
      <articleNo>제20조</articleNo>
      <title>교육</title>
      <body>&lt;div&gt;정기 안전보건교육을 실시한다.&lt;/div&gt; 개정이유: 삭제되어야 함</body>
      <effectiveFrom>2025-01-01</effectiveFrom>
      <effectiveTo>2026-01-01</effectiveTo>
    </article>
  </articles>
  <appendices>
    <appendix>
      <label>별표 1</label>
      <title>위험기계의 종류</title>
      <body>&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;프레스&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;</body>
      <effectiveFrom>2024-01-09</effectiveFrom>
    </appendix>
  </appendices>
